race.description: The Agency Property Management Maiden Handicap
race.comment: ARTGIRL (7) was rock solid in betting on debut over this trip at Wyong but just failed to pick up the top two in a tight finish. Trialled since and with that experience on board she looks hard to beat in a race that lacks a stand-out. CAFFE FLORIAN (6) copped some early interference then rallied late to get up for third in an impressive debut over this course and distance a fortnight ago. Has a wide gate to contend with but with even luck she can play a pivotal role. Price/Kent first starter IRISH WITCHY (2) easily won a recent Rosehill trial so keep him in mind. ATTRACTIVENESS (8) MONOTONE (3)
